### Get all primary location preferences
GET {{BASE_URL}}/primary-location-preferences

### Get a single primary location preference by ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/primary-location-preferences/1

### Create a new primary location preference
POST {{BASE_URL}}/primary-location-preferences
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "location": "New York",
  "preferred": true
}

### Update a primary location preference by ID
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/primary-location-preferences/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "preferred": false
}

### Delete a primary location preference by ID
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/primary-location-preferences/1
